Change Log for Nuntius Leo 0.2.1

Features:
	- Mailbox folder can be set by user

Resolved bugs:
	- Font size now is displayed and set correctly in mail editor
	- Settings-dialog is displayed again (bug 2122398)
	- Mails now are correctly sorted by date, not by day of week (bug 2122407)


Change Log for 0.2:

Features:
	- Forward, Reply and Reply All a message
	- Multipart support
	- Support for attachments

Resolved bugs:
	- Configurations are updated without restart Nuntius Leo
	- Mailfolder now should work for Windows as well



